Notes: WIAC Championship Semifinal...UWO ranked 23rd on D3hoops.com...UWO never
trails in the game...UWL cuts lead to 23-18, UWO goes on 7-0 run...UWO leads
by as many as 14 in 4th quarter, UWL cuts lead to 48-42...UWO scores last nine
points from line...UWO advances to fifth straight WIAC title game (3-1).
Game.Officials: Chuck Morning,  Tim Gilbertson,  Mark Repinski
